snippet.title: King's Knight (NES) - Player 1 Going For 1 Run
snippet.description:
What do you do if you want to play everything in a lifetime? 
Player 1 Going For 1 Run is a project where I play each game for only one run.

In this game a group of four heroes embark on a quest. They have, as you and me, one life each.
